Package com.agilebank.util.logger.service

Class TransactionServiceLogger

java.lang.Object
com.agilebank.util.logger.service.TransactionServiceLogger
@Component public class TransactionServiceLogger extends Object
AOP-enabled class that logs all calls to public methods of TransactionService. Calls to entrance, exit and exception throwing are all logged.
Author:
jason
